  SCIENCE FACTS
============================================================

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Wave Equation
Formula: v = fλ
Note:    Speed of wave = frequency × wavelength

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Boyle's Law
Formula: P₁V₁ = P₂V₂
Note:    Pressure and volume inversely proportional at constant T

Domain:  Mathematics
Topic:   Pythagorean Theorem
Formula: a² + b² = c²
Note:    Right triangle relationship; foundation of geometry

Domain:  Chemistry
Topic:   Ideal Gas Law
Formula: PV = nRT
Note:    Pressure, volume, temperature relationship for ideal gas

Domain:  Mathematics
Topic:   Bayes Theorem
Formula: P(A|B) = P(B|A)P(A)/P(B)
Note:    Updating probability based on new evidence

